window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Two cities have fallen to the Eldritch Horror, but the beastkin thirst for vengeance.</p> <p>Jake has united and empowered the beastkin into a formidable force, marching towards Life's Haven to reclaim their city and exact payback for countless lives lost.</p> <p>Yet danger lurks as enemy Champions, reptile betrayers, and a horrible curse tests their resolve. The war to reclaim the world stretches beyond a single battle, for it is an unrelenting war for survival. With the help of Jake's new beastkin mate and his bonded wives, they press on, rallying their people to face the enemy head-on.</p> <p>In this decisive moment, can Jake lead his allies to victory, or will millions suffer the consequences for his failure? The fate of their world hangs in the balance.</p> <p>Contains: LitRPG system, kingdom building, crafting, cultivation, dungeon crawling, and an infinite multiverse.</p>"; 
